{"tid":2253469,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰大裁員︱4鄉音大媽自稱中資機構職員 國泰城外派傳單「挖角」","createTime":"2020-10-22T07:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T09:20:32.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"29c7c6814dc48ab34713663ba53d6914d8e96d7a","tid":2253469,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"國泰航空昨日宣佈在港裁員5,300人，旗下的港龍航空即日停運。《蘋果》今早（22日）再次到達國泰城外視察。就現場所見，大部份員工如常上班，有保安及國泰員工於傳媒區外通道及鄰旁天橋上駐守。<br />\n<br />\n早上11時，有4名中年女士在國泰城外四處徘徊，又向現場傳媒詢問「幾時有空姐嚟呀」，其後再走近辦公室大樓，不時向身穿制服的機組人員派發單張。<br />\n<br />\n記者上前詢問，該4名女士表示她們為一間中資機構員工，並操濃厚鄉音回答：「我哋都係前一日睇到新聞，知道航空業有好多人失業，我哋都係一間中資機構嘅，內部都有好多專務嘅，（來國泰城）幫公司做個宣傳咁樣。」她們續向記者派發附有其個人卡片的宣傳單張，上面寫有「誠聘英才」及「疫情底下保証有人工加！全力支援5大行業」等字句。<br />\n<br />\n她們稱，今日到國泰城派發招聘單張是自發行為，更謂「你唔好擺上網大肆宣傳，我哋都係想幫到佢哋（國泰員工）㗎啫」，其後陸續登上一輛七人輛離去，全程逗留約半小時。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Dy2CZrLSzwslPizkQkzwx6NTwfk=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/45D75KOE4BEHHPBZ5NICNIAGH4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDy2CZrLSzwslPizkQkzwx6NTwfk%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F45D75KOE4BEHHPBZ5NICNIAGH4.JPG&h=c9ab7cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Do1i1qME-FDFnsfKLD0_-Io3eks=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NY3MYZUTXFBNFAJUYWLEEEA2OI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDo1i1qME-FDFnsfKLD0_-Io3eks%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNY3MYZUTXFBNFAJUYWLEEEA2OI.JPG&h=181ba851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tUO2KrdUsq8-oztX6Rx2--qpUl8=/802x527/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JTC3GR5RYVH2P